revisions.description: In the description of cipSecTunHistHcInDecompOctets, cipSecTunHcInOctets has been changed to cipSecTunHistHcInOctets. In the description of cipSecTunHistOutUncompOctets, cipSecTunOutOctets has been changed to cipSecTunHistOutOctets. In the description of cipSecTunHistHcOutUncompOctets, cipSecTunHcOutOctets has been changed to cipSecTunHistHcOutOctets. In the description of cipSecTunHistInDecompOctets, cipSecTunInOctets has been changed to cipSecTunHistInOctets.
Added two table for media gateway stats information: cikePhase1GWStatsTable (phase-1 IKE) cipSecPhase2GWStatsTable (phase-2 IPsec)
Changed cipSecSpiValue to Unsigned32. Changed Protocol ranges to start at 0 instead of 1. Removed comment(s) incorrectly indicating this MIB was CiscoExperiment.
Initial version of this MIB module.
